      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know u aren't a doctor but i'm just looking for a general idea. i've heard that taking smaller amounts more often is actually better for keeping the inflammation down than waiting until the pain gets bad again. like, if i take 400mg every 2 hours, wouldn't that just keep a steady level of medicine in my system? it seems more efficient than waiting 6 hours and then being in agony for a while.",
